{"tid":642650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大華裔女星 酥胸半露","createTime":"2018-04-26T02:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T00:54:47.000Z","uid":6604,"like":58,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2d7fc983ff75881171c448ce7bde8f704d226cd4","tid":642650,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"歌手鄭欣宜（Joyce）首個紅館演唱會圓滿結束兼大獲好評，呢日佢就約埋成班朋友游水慶祝。佢喺IG story上載游水短片，見佢哋一行人清一色以「黑白間條」泳衣上陣，相當有默契！而向來擁有勁爆身材嘅Joyce，着上超低胸泳衣大騷「巨峰」，仲戴埋眼鏡化身「眼鏡娘」，大玩另類誘惑，認真蠱惑！之後，Joyce仲坐喺池邊曬太陽，仲邊歎住特飲邊玩自拍添！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180425/photo/bkn-20180425162050901-0425_00862_001_04b.jpg?20180425164852\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180425%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180425162050901-0425_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20180425164852&h=1764cc47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180425/photo/bkn-20180425162050901-0425_00862_001_03b.jpg?20180425164852\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180425%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180425162050901-0425_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20180425164852&h=267cfb30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180425/photo/bkn-20180425162050901-0425_00862_001_02b.jpg?20180425164852\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180425%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180425162050901-0425_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20180425164852&h=a7599e17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9669d068b7890480078cff6939fdadd33a926f59","tid":642650,"uid":181819,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"入緊黎個陣都知奶野...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f2d6fed86778f5a33a1f28bccaa77ff7e656de","tid":642650,"uid":85451,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0